gomodel:SYNGO_1605  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Literal: \"In dendritic spines, the postsynaptic density of glutamatergic-like, excitatory synapses was distinctly reactive (Fig. 2 A-C). Perisynaptic α7-nAChRs (i.e., localized within a 50-nm halo around the synaptic disk) were found flanking glutamatergic and nonglutamatergic synapses\"\n\nNote: antibodies and labeled akphaBtx were used for detection.. Experimental description: \"This study used a total of 16 rhesus macaques (Macaca mulatta):\"" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0593-3443" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" ;
